            "detailed_description": "<strong>Grand Class Melee 2</strong> is an RPG job system arena fighter featuring a huge roster of over 60 character classes to battle with. Drawing inspiration from JRPG favorites and the competitive classics of console multiplayer, players progress through 8 intensifying rounds of fierce combat, gain new abilities each round and build up their arsenals to the top of the class tree.<br><br>To bolster the slash/thrust/parry weapons-based melee, every player pairs the new ability of their chosen job with one earned from an earlier job for an ever-evolving, two-fisted loadout. <i>With up to 4 players mixing &amp; matching, the possibilities are sprawling!</i><br><br>The fight gets fleshed out further by <strong>bots</strong>, <strong>teams</strong>, <strong>custom scoring</strong>, <strong>deeply tweakable procedurally generated battlefields</strong> and beyond with additional gameplay options.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/340440/extras/gcm2_monsters_giffy_alt_04.png?t=1532095483\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><strong>GCM2</strong> offers a highly-customizable local-multiplayer brawl supporting up to 4 players on gamepads &amp; keyboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Features currently available include:</u></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>'Critters'</strong> wander each biome, dropping a heart when killed (live as of <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/1344737036195822514\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.7!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'Selection Hiding'</strong> to prevent opponents from counter-picking classes (live as of <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/599373548487112944\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.4!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'Terrain Generation Customization'</strong> that gives players the power to deeply customize the terrain generator (live as of <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/881963009554931449\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.2!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'Steam Workshop Class Tree Modding'</strong> that gives players the power to create &amp; customize classes (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/876327643175549124\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.0!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'AI Challenges'</strong> with leaderboard support to bring fame to your hard-fought victories (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/899960909703771706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.16</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/111813217706511594\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.14</a>!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Achievements &amp; Trading Cards'</strong> to round out the Steam game experience (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/899960909703771706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.16</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/160222811882368631\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.13</a>!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Spectator Mode'</strong> to set the AI on autopilot and relax as the melee unfolds (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/160219302120778806\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.12</a>!)</li></ul><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/340440/extras/gcm2_updated_store_banner.png?t=1532095483\" ><br><br>In the tradition of Street Fighter II, Warcraft II, Bomberman 2, Seiken Densetsu 2 and other greats you may not have played until they hit with part two, we present <strong>Grand Class Melee 2</strong> - a game for those who like a little variety in their job system arena combat.",
            "about_the_game": "<strong>Grand Class Melee 2</strong> is an RPG job system arena fighter featuring a huge roster of over 60 character classes to battle with. Drawing inspiration from JRPG favorites and the competitive classics of console multiplayer, players progress through 8 intensifying rounds of fierce combat, gain new abilities each round and build up their arsenals to the top of the class tree.<br><br>To bolster the slash/thrust/parry weapons-based melee, every player pairs the new ability of their chosen job with one earned from an earlier job for an ever-evolving, two-fisted loadout. <i>With up to 4 players mixing &amp; matching, the possibilities are sprawling!</i><br><br>The fight gets fleshed out further by <strong>bots</strong>, <strong>teams</strong>, <strong>custom scoring</strong>, <strong>deeply tweakable procedurally generated battlefields</strong> and beyond with additional gameplay options.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/340440/extras/gcm2_monsters_giffy_alt_04.png?t=1532095483\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><strong>GCM2</strong> offers a highly-customizable local-multiplayer brawl supporting up to 4 players on gamepads &amp; keyboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Features currently available include:</u></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>'Critters'</strong> wander each biome, dropping a heart when killed (live as of <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/1344737036195822514\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.7!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'Selection Hiding'</strong> to prevent opponents from counter-picking classes (live as of <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/599373548487112944\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.4!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'Terrain Generation Customization'</strong> that gives players the power to deeply customize the terrain generator (live as of <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/881963009554931449\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.2!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'Steam Workshop Class Tree Modding'</strong> that gives players the power to create &amp; customize classes (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/876327643175549124\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.1.0!</a>)<br></li><li> <strong>'AI Challenges'</strong> with leaderboard support to bring fame to your hard-fought victories (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/899960909703771706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.16</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/111813217706511594\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.14</a>!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Achievements &amp; Trading Cards'</strong> to round out the Steam game experience (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/899960909703771706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.16</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/160222811882368631\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.13</a>!)<br></li><li> <strong>'Spectator Mode'</strong> to set the AI on autopilot and relax as the melee unfolds (live as of <a href=\"http://steamcommunity.com/games/340440/announcements/detail/160219302120778806\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >v1.0.12</a>!)</li></ul><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/340440/extras/gcm2_updated_store_banner.png?t=1532095483\" ><br><br>In the tradition of Street Fighter II, Warcraft II, Bomberman 2, Seiken Densetsu 2 and other greats you may not have played until they hit with part two, we present <strong>Grand Class Melee 2</strong> - a game for those who like a little variety in their job system arena combat.",
